NK080(wu)033:1: // gnas lung chen mo'i tho yig bzhugs so //
NK080(wu)033:2: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK080(wu)033:3: brten na srid dang rtsol ba yis //
NK080(wu)033:4: sdug bsngal grol 'gyur rnams la mos //
NK080(wu)033:5: ma goms mdzad spyod mi 'khrul phyir //
NK080(wu)033:6: snying po gnas kyi chog tho pri //
NK080(wu)033:7: dkyil 'khor bdun dang bsnyen sgrub bzhi //
NK080(wu)033:8: dbu zhabs don du shes par bya //
NK080(wu)033:10: gang byed gnas su stegs bu brtsigs //
NK080(wu)033:11: sa chog bdag nyid lhar bskyed la //
NK080(wu)033:12: sngags rgya ting 'dzin stong nyid sbyang //
NK080(wu)033:13: dbang chen dur khrod gzhal yas bskyed //
NK080(wu)033:14: dam rdzas lnga yi chag chag gdab //
NK080(wu)033:15: ye shes thig la 'bru gsum sbyang //
NK080(wu)033:16: gzhal yas khang dang rigs lngar bskyed //
NK080(wu)033:17: dbang byin dbab drang bstim brtan la //
NK080(wu)033:18: kun bzang zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol dang //
NK080(wu)033:19: sman raka gtor mas mchod la bstod //
NK080(wu)033:20: bsgrims la ma ti'i sngags kyis btab //
NK080(wu)033:21: be kra yam 'degs dam tshig la //
NK080(wu)033:22: sbyangs la 'bru gsum rab gnas sgrib //
NK080(wu)033:23: badz+rasa cha chen cha phran gdab //
NK080(wu)033:24: tshon la h'u zung lnga bkod sbyang //
NK080(wu)033:25: gzhan yang khro ba'i rigs lnga bskyed //
NK080(wu)033:26: dag nas bstod pa khro bos bya //
NK080(wu)033:28: bris la sku gsung thugs gzugs bkod //
NK080(wu)033:29: bsod nams gtor sbyin dkyil 'khor la //
NK080(wu)033:30: dri ma bcas la mtshan byang bri //
NK080(wu)033:31: gu gul spos bdug khrus ldan bya //
NK080(wu)033:32: cha gsum gser skyems bla glud btang //
NK080(wu)033:33: thugs rje gu gul spos dud bdug /bsang sbyang gzhal yas lhar bcas bskyed //
NK080(wu)033:34: dbang nas bstod par thig bzhin bya //
NK080(wu)033:35: tshig brjod bkod la sngags kyis bstan //
NK080(wu)033:37: khro rol mtshams bcad gzugs brnyan la //
NK080(wu)033:38: bsang sbyang rim brtsegs yig 'brus bskyed //
NK080(wu)033:39: sngags kyis gzhal yas lhar bskyed nas //
NK080(wu)033:40: dbang byin snyan dbab spyan drangs bstim //
NK080(wu)033:41: brtan bzhugs kun bzang zhabs bsil bsnol //
NK080(wu)033:42: sman gtor mchod bstod khro gzhung spyar //
NK080(wu)033:43: bum pa rdor dbyings dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK080(wu)033:44: dngos la dpal bskyed bden pa bdar //
NK080(wu)033:45: gu gul bdug la b+hi shwas bskrad //
NK080(wu)033:46: brgyad pa'i sngags brjod spos kyis bdug /sbyangs la khro bo'i gzhal yas bskyed //
NK080(wu)033:47: nyungs blug ra drug sngags kyis bskyed //
NK080(wu)033:48: de steng zhi ba'i gzhal yas bskyed //
NK080(wu)033:49: kun bzang arga mi bskyod snying //
NK080(wu)033:50: rnam snang 'byung ldan sman rin chen //
NK080(wu)033:51: mtha' yas don grub 'bru spos blug /sems dpa' mgul mchings sgo bas ni //
NK080(wu)033:52: kha rgyan thub drug gzungs thag gdags //
NK080(wu)033:53: de ltar zhi gnyis bskyed pa la //
NK080(wu)033:54: dbang byin dbabs drang bstim brtan bya //
NK080(wu)033:55: kun bsil bzhing bsnol sman gtor mchod //
NK080(wu)033:56: bstod bskor tshig dang sngags kyis brtan //
NK080(wu)033:57: skabs bya gcig dpral shes dgug spyod //
NK080(wu)033:58: cha med kun zhu brda' sgo dbye //
NK080(wu)033:59: brda' phyag bskor gsol sgrib sbyangs bskyed //
NK080(wu)033:60: bsrung dang dam bca' bsnyen par gsungs //
NK080(wu)033:61: nye bsnyen bsgrub rtsi'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK080(wu)033:62: mtshams bshags dam bca' byin mchod brlabs //
NK080(wu)033:63: zhi ba gzhung mthun khro bo yi //
NK080(wu)033:64: khang bskyed gsal gdab bdag gzhan sras //
NK080(wu)033:65: phyag dang phyag rgya bdud rtsi sman //
NK080(wu)033:66: dgongs gsol skabs dang brgyad du bsgyur //
NK080(wu)033:67: 'dod don gsol nas zhi khror bsgyur //
NK080(wu)033:68: gceg dpral shes dgug spyo ba bya //
NK080(wu)033:69: zhi khro phyag 'tshal brgya brjod bskor //
NK080(wu)033:70: gsal gdab sgrib bral lhar bskyed bsrung //
NK080(wu)033:71: dgu ni skabs su bab pa'o //
NK080(wu)033:72: dzab bstod spar chung rgyud lung bshags //
NK080(wu)033:73: tshogs mchod sku skal bsngosa la rol //
NK080(wu)033:74: gsum lnga bdun bya nye bsnyen no //
NK080(wu)033:75: tha ma mchod dang ting 'dzin bstar //
NK080(wu)033:76: 'dul sbyong sgrol dbang rdzas tshang bsog /lha bshos ting los dkyil 'khor bskor //
NK080(wu)033:77: las gzhug khro bor dril bar bya //
NK080(wu)033:78: thun mtshams gnyis ka dzab khro bo //
NK080(wu)033:79: spar chung bshags med tshogs mchod rgyas //
NK080(wu)033:80: sgrub pa'i rim pa yin par bzhed //
NK080(wu)033:81: sgrub pa chen po'i rim pa ni //
NK080(wu)033:82: rgyu drug sgrol ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi //
NK080(wu)033:83: kun tu 'od ma khro bo yi //
NK080(wu)033:84: dkyil 'khor gsal gdab gceg dbral dgug /sgrib bral lung gi tshad ma la //
NK080(wu)033:85: 'gro lnga'i sgo bcad spyi bcad smon //
NK080(wu)033:86: 'byung sgo bkag la dpal du bskyed //
NK080(wu)033:87: thod pa'i rgyan bya khrag tu dmigs //
NK080(wu)033:88: tshig bskul sngags kyis lan gsum rngub //
NK080(wu)033:89: skye rgyud bcad la gnas lngar ru //
NK080(wu)033:90: gdan lngar sa bon zung drug bkod //
NK080(wu)033:91: 'bru lnga yas bkod lung gis bskul //
NK080(wu)033:92: mas sbyangs stong 'gyur nyi shu lnga //
NK080(wu)033:93: sa la bsgral ba ye shes kyi //
NK080(wu)033:94: 'byung gsum gis sbyar lung gis bskul //
NK080(wu)033:95: stug po bkod la gru gsum bri //
NK080(wu)033:96: mtshan byang bcad la dri nang gzhug /gzhal yas lha dang bcas pa bskyed //
NK080(wu)033:97: e ram snod dang dz+wa la ram bcud //
NK080(wu)033:98: khro bor bskyod cing las la gzud //
NK080(wu)033:99: sprul pa spros la ru tra dgug /rten la dbye bstim mu dras bcing //
NK080(wu)033:100: zhing dbyug bsgyel la kha tam gtug /snying gar bsdigs mdzub gtad la bskul //
NK080(wu)033:101: sgrol ging lag g.yas ral gri gsum //
NK080(wu)033:102: bdud rtsil rim pas ta kri dang //
NK080(wu)033:104: spyan drangs gsol gdab sngags kyis bsgral //
NK080(wu)033:105: mtshan byang lag gzung tshig gsal gdab //
NK080(wu)033:106: rigs drug sa bon h'u gis sbyangs //
NK080(wu)033:107: rig pa h'u gyur dgod tshig gis //
NK080(wu)033:108: rdul tshon dbus dgod mtshan byang bzhag /pad+ma can gyi gtso bo yi //
NK080(wu)033:109: shangs rngub rim brgyud mkha' la babs //
NK080(wu)033:110: lnga ldan h'u gyur lung gis bskul //
NK080(wu)033:111: 'khor lo tshogs chen mda' gzhu la //
NK080(wu)033:112: dri chab kyis bsang yig 'bru las //
NK080(wu)033:113: lha bskyed lung dgu'i rtse la bsgral //
NK080(wu)033:114: made'u rtses blangs la h'u bsams te //
NK080(wu)033:115: shangs rngub rim brgyud tshig brjod de //
NK080(wu)033:116: cho gas lha bskyed spyi gtsug du //
NK080(wu)033:117: ye shes ldan pa zla rlung bdeg /sngags kyi thugs rje'i dal gsal gdab //
NK080(wu)033:118: rtog tshogs zhi gnyis lha la gdab //
NK080(wu)033:119: tshig dang sngags kyis lding bu yi //
NK080(wu)033:120: steng dgod sngon gyi thugs dam bskul //
NK080(wu)033:121: ye shes bla ma'i spar ba ni //
NK080(wu)033:122: me long nang du bdud rtsi blugs //
NK080(wu)033:123: b+ho d+hi'i sngags brjod mtheb srin gyis //
NK080(wu)033:124: gtor ma lung gi don gsal gdab //
NK080(wu)033:126: gzugs skur bskyed la byin gyis brlabs //
NK080(wu)033:127: 'gro don bskul la mtshan byang dbab //
NK080(wu)033:128: dri gzhugs gdan bzhag don dbang bskur //
NK080(wu)033:129: dbu rgyan gsang spyang tshig sngags kyis //
NK080(wu)033:130: rasna khang du lnga bsam mo //
NK080(wu)033:131: ye shes lnga yi tshig sngags kyis //
NK080(wu)033:132: bum rten rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan la //
NK080(wu)033:133: bden pa bdar la smon lam gdab //
NK080(wu)033:134: phreng ba bsang sbyangs rab gnas ldan //
NK080(wu)033:135: tshig dang sngags brjod smon lam mo //
NK080(wu)033:136: dkyil 'khor steng bzhag mar me dbul //
NK080(wu)033:137: ma 'ongs don la gar gyi bro //
NK080(wu)033:138: lha mo bcu gnyis phar mchod de //
NK080(wu)033:139: su re to ni skyes lan tshul //
NK080(wu)033:140: 'dod yon zhing gzhung bzhin du dbul //
NK080(wu)033:141: mar me'i smon lam rgyud lung gi //
NK080(wu)033:142: bshags pa bya zhing byang bu bsreg /snying po gnas kyis smon lam gdab //
NK080(wu)033:143: lhag btang brtan skyong dri ma bshig /dge bsdo dal bsdu lhar bskyed de //
NK080(wu)033:144: bro bya go bgo lus srung dang //
NK080(wu)033:145: dbang bskur cod pan phreng ba dang //
NK080(wu)033:146: dges bskyed bshags la bka' drin gsol //
NK080(wu)033:147: spyod lam rgyu gnas gtang rag btang //
NK080(wu)033:148: dkyil 'khor bdun la zhi bsnyen pa //
NK080(wu)033:149: gcig la nye bsnyen bsgrub par sbyar //
NK080(wu)033:150: gnyis ni sgrub pa chen po'o //
NK080(wu)033:151: mdzad spyod rnam pa gsum gsungs te //
NK080(wu)033:152: dang po gces dpral shes pa dgug /bar pa bsgrib
NK080(wu)033:153: sbyong tshogs bsag go /tha ma gnas spar dbang bskur
NK080(wu)033:154: ro // gnas lung chen mo'i tho yig pan+di ta bi ma las sbyar ba'o //
